let's get on the ship.

105
00:11:02,180 --> 00:11:03,220
Uncle San Xing is very experienced.

106
00:11:03,300 --> 00:11:05,000
Unless the device in
your ship is broken,

107
00:11:05,007 --> 00:11:06,347
