sell the stuff on the ship.

187
00:15:19,915 --> 00:15:22,747
As long as I'm having
a good time, I'm happy.

188
00:15:23,143 --> 00:15:24,352
Come on, we hardly met.

189
00:15:24,365 --> 00:15:25,658
