273
00:18:31,815 --> 00:18:33,055
I was just lucky.

274
00:18:33,380 --> 00:18:35,480
I happened to publish a few articles,

275
00:18:36,040 --> 00:18:37,720
and made some minor achievements.

276
00:18:37,755 --> 00:18:39,075
